{"lemma":"فُرْقَة","slug":"فُرْقَة","root":"ف.ر.ق","root_slug":"ف-ر-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ر-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"فُرْقَة","root":"فرق","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":10},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n33657","n33670","n33671"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"part, portion"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"troop of people, number of men, distinct body"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"division, detachment, section, unit"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"party, group, band, company"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sect"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"class"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"class (in school)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a separate herd"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a portion of a thing in a state of dispersion"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"separation"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From ف ر ق (f r q); compare فَرَقَ (faraqa, “to separate”)."},"ipa":["/fir.qa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n33657","headword_ar":"فرّقهُ","root":"frq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taforiyqN","text_ar":"تَفْرِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taforiqapN","text_ar":"تَفْرِقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He separated it"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into several,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"many, portions"},{"kind":"text","text":"];"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disunited it"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. a thing, or a collection of things]; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dispersed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dissipated, it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or did so"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"greatly"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"widely"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bad~adahu","text_ar":"بَدَّدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fr~q bayona","text_ar":"فرّق بَيْنَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^a$oyaA='i","text_ar":"الاَشْيَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caused, a separation"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wide, separation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between the things"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhimo fr~qhu","text_ar":"فِيهِمْ فرّقهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohimo","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِمْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He scattered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distributed, it among them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to them."},{"kind":"text","text":"] See 1, former half, in five places. It is said in a trad. of 'Omar,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"far~iquwA Eani Almaniy~api waA@joEaluwA","text_ar":"فَرِّقُوا عَنِ المَنِيَّةِ وَا@جْعَلُوا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~aA^osa raA^osayoni","text_ar":"الرَّاْسَ رَاْسَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, O, *) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Separate ye"},{"kind":"text","text":"your cattle by way of preservation"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from death,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and make the one head two head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] by buying two animals with the price of one, that, when one dies, the second may remain. (Mgh, O.) And it is said in a trad. respecting the poor-rate,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA","text_ar":"لَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yufar~aqu bayona mujotamiEK walaA yujomaEu bayona mufotariqK","text_ar":"يُفَرَّقُ بَيْنَ مُجْتَمِعٍ وَلَا يُجْمَعُ بَيْنَ مُفْتَرِقٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There shall be no separating what is put together, nor shall"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2384},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"there be a putting together what is separate."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. [The reason is, that by either of these acts, in the case of cattle, the amount of the poor-rate may be diminished.])"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yufar~iquwna bihi bayona A@lomaro'i wazawojihi","text_ar":"يُفَرِّقُونَ بِهِ بَيْنَ ا@لْمَرْءِ وَزَوْجِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the Kur ii. 96, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whereby they might dissolve, break up, discompose, derange, disorganize, disorder,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsettle, the state of union subsisting between the man and his wife, in respect of affairs and of the expression of opinion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, briefly,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whereby they might cause division and dissension between the man and his wife,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Altaforiyqu","text_ar":"التَفْرِيقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta$otiytu Al$~amoli waAlkalimapi","text_ar":"تَشْتِيتُ الشَّمْلِ وَالكَلِمَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (El-Isbahánee, TA.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fr~q AlA^amora","text_ar":"فرّق الاَمْرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$at~atahu","text_ar":"شَتَّتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He discomposed, deranged, disorganized, disordered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsettled, the state of affairs"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$t","text_ar":"شت"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fr~q EalayonaA AlkalaAma","text_ar":"فرّق عَلَيْنَا الكَلَامَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He scattered speech"},{"kind":"text","text":"(app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he jabbered"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at us,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"against us"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bq","text_ar":"بق"},{"kind":"text","text":": see R. Q. 1 in that art.) In the saying in the Kur [ii. 130 and iii. 78],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA nufar~iqu bayona A^aHadK minohumo","text_ar":"لَا نُفَرِّقُ بَيْنَ اَحَدٍ مِنْهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We will not make a distinction between any of them"},{"kind":"text","text":"], the verb is allowably made to relate to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHd","text_ar":"احد"},{"kind":"text","text":"because this word [in negative phrases] imports a pl. meaning. (TA. [See p. 27, 3rd col.]) See, again, 1, near the middle.       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fr~qhu","text_ar":"فرّقهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taforiyqN","text_ar":"تَفْرِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K, TA,) also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him to fear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be afraid; put him in fear;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"frightened him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, * TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minohu","text_ar":"مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aforaqotuhu","text_ar":"اَفْرَقْتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I made him to fear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be afraid of, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and Lh mentions"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlSabiY~a","text_ar":"الصَبِىَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraqotu","text_ar":"فَرَقْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I frightened the boy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"child;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but ISd says, I think it to be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"far~aqotu","text_ar":"فَرَّقْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n33670","headword_ar":"فُرْقَةٌ","root":"frq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"the subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAraqahu","text_ar":"فَارَقَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, MA, * TA;) or from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aifotaraqa","text_ar":"اِفْتَرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) [i. e.] a quasi-inf. n. used in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AifotiraAqN","text_ar":"اِفْتِرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Separation, disunion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abandonment;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, KL, PS;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraAqN","text_ar":"فَرَاقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is syn. therewith, whence the reading [in the Kur xviii. 77],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA faraAqu bayoniY wabayonika","text_ar":"هٰذَا فَرَاقُ بَيْنِى وَبَيْنِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This"},{"kind":"text","text":"shall be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the separation of my and thy union"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and so is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firaAqN","text_ar":"فِرَاقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, * K, TA,) which [is an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fArqh","text_ar":"فارقه"},{"kind":"text","text":", and], in the Kur lxxv. 28, means the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"time of the quitting of the present world by death."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n33671","headword_ar":"فِرْقَةٌ","root":"frq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAy^ifap","text_ar":"طَايِفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party, portion, division, sect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distinct body"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"class,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of men, (S, O, Msb, K,) and of other things; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firoqN","text_ar":"فِرْقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) and so, accord. to IB, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariyqN","text_ar":"فَرِيقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA: [but see this last word:]) [and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a separate herd"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"of cattle:] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firaqN","text_ar":"فِرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aforaAqN","text_ar":"اَفْرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K) is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firaqN","text_ar":"فِرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afaAriyqu","text_ar":"اَفَارِيقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aforaAqN","text_ar":"اَفْرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afaAriqapN","text_ar":"اَفَارِقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs in poetry; (O, K;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afaAriyqu","text_ar":"اَفَارِيقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be of the class of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abaATiylu","text_ar":"اَبَاطِيلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a pl. without a sing. (O, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A portion of a thing in a state of dispersion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firoqN","text_ar":"فِرْقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariyqN","text_ar":"فَرِيقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L, TA.)       -A2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A skin that is full"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of milk"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that cannot be agitated to make butter"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hat~aY","text_ar":"حَتَّى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aYo yu*oraqa","text_ar":"اَىْ يُذْرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuforaqa","text_ar":"يُفْرَقَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. a tropical phrase meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"until it is made to void some of its contents"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K"]}]}}